---
// AgileCoachLayoffsTimeline.astro
// Drop into src/components/ and reference in your post
// Usage: <AgileCoachLayoffsTimeline />
//
// Vertical stack of Agile coach and PM-role layoff events from
// January 2023 through mid-May 2026. Click a row to expand its body
// and reveal the source link. One row open at a time. No hover.
---

<div class="acl-wrapper" id="acl-timeline">
  <div class="acl-header">
    <h3 class="acl-title">The Cascade: Agile Coach and PM Role Layoffs, 2023 to 2026</h3>
    <p class="acl-subtitle">Named events and aggregate tech-sector totals. Click any row to expand.</p>
  </div>

  <ol class="acl-list">

    <li class="acl-row named">
      <button class="acl-row-btn" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="acl-row-marker"></div>
        <div class="acl-row-summary">
          <div class="acl-row-head">
            <span class="acl-row-date">January 2023</span>
            <span class="acl-row-tag">Named event</span>
          </div>
          <div class="acl-row-line">
            <span class="acl-row-company">Capital One</span>
            <span class="acl-row-count">~1,100 roles</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="acl-row-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
      </button>
      <div class="acl-row-body">
        <p>Eliminated the entire Agile job family: Scrum Masters, Agile Coaches, Agile Delivery Leads, Agile Portfolio Leads. Roles absorbed into engineering and product management.</p>
        <a class="acl-row-source" href="https://www.computerweekly.com/news/252529477/More-than-1000-tech-roles-chopped-at-Capital-One" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source: Computer Weekly</a>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="acl-row named">
      <button class="acl-row-btn" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="acl-row-marker"></div>
        <div class="acl-row-summary">
          <div class="acl-row-head">
            <span class="acl-row-date">December 2023</span>
            <span class="acl-row-tag">Named event</span>
          </div>
          <div class="acl-row-line">
            <span class="acl-row-company">Spotify</span>
            <span class="acl-row-count">1,500 roles (17% of staff)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="acl-row-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
      </button>
      <div class="acl-row-body">
        <p>CEO Daniel Ek's memo cited too many people doing work around the work rather than delivering for stakeholders. The coach-layer rationale, stated by the CEO.</p>
        <a class="acl-row-source" href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/12/04/spotify-to-lay-off-17percent-of-employees-ceo-daniel-ek-says.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source: CNBC</a>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="acl-row aggregate">
      <button class="acl-row-btn" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="acl-row-marker"></div>
        <div class="acl-row-summary">
          <div class="acl-row-head">
            <span class="acl-row-date">Full Year 2025</span>
            <span class="acl-row-tag">Sector aggregate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="acl-row-line">
            <span class="acl-row-company">Tech sector total</span>
            <span class="acl-row-count">~246,000 jobs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="acl-row-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
      </button>
      <div class="acl-row-body">
        <p>Layoffs.fyi tracked nearly a quarter million tech jobs cut in 2025. Roughly 55,000 explicitly AI-attributed in the US alone.</p>
        <a class="acl-row-source" href="https://www.informationweek.com/it-staffing-careers/2026-tech-company-layoffs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source: InformationWeek</a>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="acl-row named">
      <button class="acl-row-btn" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="acl-row-marker"></div>
        <div class="acl-row-summary">
          <div class="acl-row-head">
            <span class="acl-row-date">March 2026</span>
            <span class="acl-row-tag">Named event</span>
          </div>
          <div class="acl-row-line">
            <span class="acl-row-company">Atlassian</span>
            <span class="acl-row-count">1,600 roles (10% of workforce)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="acl-row-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
      </button>
      <div class="acl-row-body">
        <p>Cuts concentrated in content creation, customer support, quality assurance, and project management. 800 net new roles announced in AI engineering, ML ops, and AI safety.</p>
        <a class="acl-row-source" href="https://www.metaintro.com/blog/atlassian-1600-layoffs-ceo-contradicts-ai-pivot-tech-workers-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source: Metaintro</a>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="acl-row aggregate">
      <button class="acl-row-btn" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="acl-row-marker"></div>
        <div class="acl-row-summary">
          <div class="acl-row-head">
            <span class="acl-row-date">Through Mid-May 2026</span>
            <span class="acl-row-tag">Sector aggregate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="acl-row-line">
            <span class="acl-row-company">Tech sector year-to-date</span>
            <span class="acl-row-count">~128,000 jobs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="acl-row-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
      </button>
      <div class="acl-row-body">
        <p>Roughly 1,000 tech jobs cut per day on average. Pace exceeds 2025. PM, QA, and content categories disproportionately represented.</p>
        <a class="acl-row-source" href="https://www.trueup.io/layoffs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source: TrueUp Layoffs Tracker</a>
      </div>
    </li>

  </ol>
</div>

<style>
  .acl-wrapper {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px 20px 20px 20px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  }

  .acl-header {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .acl-title {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .acl-subtitle {
    color: #aaaaaa;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .acl-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .acl-list::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 7px;
    top: 14px;
    bottom: 14px;
    width: 2px;
    background: #2e2e2e;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .acl-row {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #232323;
    border: 1px solid #333333;
    border-left: 3px solid #c44545;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .acl-row.aggregate {
    border-left-color: #4a7fa8;
  }

  .acl-row:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .acl-row-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    text-align: left;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: inherit;
    font: inherit;
    position: relative;
  }

  .acl-row-btn:focus {
    outline: none;
  }

  .acl-row-btn:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .acl-row-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #c44545;
    border: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #2a2a2a;
    margin-left: -8px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .acl-row.aggregate .acl-row-marker {
    background: #4a7fa8;
  }

  .acl-row.acl-open .acl-row-marker {
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }

  .acl-row-summary {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .acl-row-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .acl-row-date {
    color: #aaaaaa;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .acl-row-tag {
    color: #777777;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .acl-row-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .acl-row-company {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .acl-row-count {
    color: #c44545;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .acl-row.aggregate .acl-row-count {
    color: #4a7fa8;
  }

  .acl-row-chevron {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #888888;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    width: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .acl-row.acl-open .acl-row-chevron {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .acl-row-body {
    color: #dddddd;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0 14px 0 44px;
    transition: max-height 0.25s ease, padding 0.25s ease;
  }

  .acl-row-body p {
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .acl-row-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .acl-row.acl-open .acl-row-body {
    max-height: 300px;
    padding: 0 14px 14px 44px;
  }

  .acl-row-source {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #8ab4d8;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a7fa8;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .acl-row-source:hover {
    color: #b8d4ee;
    border-bottom-color: #b8d4ee;
  }

  .acl-row.named .acl-row-source {
    color: #e89a9a;
    border-bottom-color: #c44545;
  }

  .acl-row.named .acl-row-source:hover {
    color: #f0bcbc;
    border-bottom-color: #f0bcbc;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .acl-wrapper {
      padding: 20px 16px 16px 16px;
    }
    .acl-row-btn {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .acl-row-company {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .acl-row-body {
      font-size: 12px;
      padding-left: 38px;
    }
    .acl-row.acl-open .acl-row-body {
      padding: 0 12px 12px 38px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  function initAclTimeline() {
    const wrapper = document.getElementById('acl-timeline');
    if (!wrapper) return;

    // Guard against double-init if both event listeners fire
    if (wrapper.dataset.aclInitialized === 'true') return;
    wrapper.dataset.aclInitialized = 'true';

    const rows = wrapper.querySelectorAll('.acl-row');
    const buttons = wrapper.querySelectorAll('.acl-row-btn');

    function closeAll() {
      rows.forEach((row) => {
        row.classList.remove('acl-open');
        const btn = row.querySelector('.acl-row-btn');
        if (btn) btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      });
    }

    buttons.forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.stopPropagation();
        const row = btn.closest('.acl-row');
        if (!row) return;
        const isOpen = row.classList.contains('acl-open');
        closeAll();
        if (!isOpen) {
          row.classList.add('acl-open');
          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
        }
      });
    });

    document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (!wrapper.contains(e.target)) {
        closeAll();
      }
    });

    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
      if (e.key === 'Escape') closeAll();
    });
  }

  // Fire on standard DOM ready (no View Transitions)
  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initAclTimeline);
  } else {
    initAclTimeline();
  }

  // Fire on Astro View Transitions navigation (if enabled)
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', initAclTimeline);
</script>